item.title: A Good Move from MacOS
item.description: This thing is available under their website for each app, a good thing to be added in terms of privacy concern whether the app is collecting your data or not. And yes, it’s on their website called App privacy. Here’s a bit on their website Data collection The purpose of the label is to help your customers understand what data is collected from your app and how it is used.
